🚀 Ride the cosmic wave with #SILVERSURFER!

From the farthest reaches of the cosmos, Norrin Radd arrives, wielding the boundless Power Cosmic. Witness the Herald's grace and devastating power as he surfs through shattered realities.
Bend the very fabric of existence to your will. Embrace the Power Cosmic in MARVEL Mystic Mayhem!

description:
Play MARVEL Cosmic Invasion’s demo NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2753970/MARVEL_Cosmic_Invasion/ 

Jump into the action with 9 iconic heroes: She-Hulk, Rocket Raccoon, Venom, Phyla-Vell, Spider-Man, Storm, Wolverine, Nova, and Captain America, and take on epic battles across Marvel’s New York City and the Helicarrier in this fast-paced demo! 

From New York City to the depths of the Negative Zone, the future of the universe will be fought for across the stars in MARVEL Cosmic Invasion!
